Package org.kynosarges.tektosyne.demo

Contains the Tektosyne Demo application.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AboutDialog
    Shows a modal dialog with information about the application.
    BenchmarkDialog
    Provides a dialog for benchmarking several Tektosyne algorithms.
    ConvexHullDialog
    Provides a dialog for testing the GeoUtils.convexHull(org.kynosarges.tektosyne.geometry.PointD...) algorithm.
    DesktopAction
    Encapsulates AWT Desktop actions.
    DoubleStringConverter
    Converts between user-edited strings and Double values.
    Global
    Provides global resources and helpers for the application.
    GraphDialog
    Provides a dialog for testing Graph algorithms.
    IntegerStringConverter
    Converts between user-edited strings and Integer values.
    LineIntersectionDialog
    Provides a dialog for testing the brute force MultiLineIntersection algorithm.
    MakeGridDialog
    Provides a dialog for printing and saving PolygonGrid instances.
    PointInPolygonDialog
    Provides a dialog for testing the GeoUtils.pointInPolygon(org.kynosarges.tektosyne.geometry.PointD, org.kynosarges.tektosyne.geometry.PointD[]) algorithm.
    PolygonGridDialog
    Provides a dialog for testing the PolygonGrid class.
    RegularPolygonDialog
    Provides a dialog for testing the RegularPolygon class.
    SubdivisionDialog
    Provides a dialog for testing the Subdivision class.
    SubdivisionInterDialog
    Provides a dialog for testing the Subdivision.intersection(org.kynosarges.tektosyne.subdivision.Subdivision, org.kynosarges.tektosyne.subdivision.Subdivision) algorithm of the Subdivision class.
    TektosyneDemo
    Defines the Tektosyne Demo application for JavaFX.
    VoronoiDialog
    Provides a dialog for testing the Voronoi algorithm.
